### Get all usuarios
GET http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios

###

### Create usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "senha": "password"
}

###

### Get usuario by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios/1

###

### Update usuario
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "senha": "newpassword"
}

###

### Delete usuario
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios/1

###

### Get all turmas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/turmas

###

### Create turma
POST http://localhost:3000/api/turmas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Turma A",
  "alunos": "João, Maria"
}

###

### Get turma by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/turmas/1

###

### Update turma
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/turmas/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Turma B",
  "alunos": "Pedro, Ana"
}

###

### Delete turma
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/turmas/1

###

### Get all ucs
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ucs

###

### Create uc
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ucs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Unidade Curricular 1",
  "link_diario": "http://example.com/diario"
}

###

### Get uc by id
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ucs/1

###

### Update uc
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/ucs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Unidade Curricular 2",
  "link_diario": "http://example.com/diario2"
}

###

